<br>
Ro didnt get her last name until she was in her mid 20's. For two reasons really... my sister would (obviously) share the name so we had to find a last name we would agree on... and for the longest time we could only agree on Duh'Postrophie. But we decided that since this is the Roleplay server, and we are dark elves that would be somewhat rude /grin. Then we found one we LOVED but the gms wouldnt let us have it. So we just kinda wandered around until we found a really great word to use. Mecurial has all kinds of yummy meanings so voila... thats what it is.<br>
<br>
I think a surname gives more depth to a character. I feel like my girls are more &quot;real&quot; with two names. <br>
<br>
Whenever I make a character, I sit at the creation screen and I think of both names. And some of them are just too fabulous. I wont tell you the good ones, because that will kill my &quot;Im not telling you who i was in a past life, 'cause im not that person anymore&quot; thing I have going on... <br>
